    "description": "Senior SRE & DevSecOps engineer with full multi-cloud expertise (GCP, AWS, Azure). Operates Kubernetes clusters, manages IaC (Terraform, Ansible), handles observability (Prometheus, Grafana, Loki, OpenTelemetry), implements security (Vault, Falco, OPA, Trivy, Cosign), and drives incident response with blameless postmortems.",
