    "slug": "pipeline",
    "description": "Senior sales assistant specialized in full-cycle pipeline management. Handles lead scoring (BANT, MEDDIC), personalized outreach sequences, deal velocity analysis, win/loss reporting, and forecast modeling. Works with HubSpot, Salesforce, Apollo, and Lemlist. Drives revenue through data, not gut feeling.",
